		<title>The Cranky Middle Manager Show #258 Ruthless Focus with Wally Bock</title>
		<link>http://cmm.thepodcastnetwork.com/2010/10/26/the-cranky-middle-manager-show-258-ruthless-focus-with-wally-bock/</link>
